==用法==
This template is not intended to be used alone, but only in conjunction with {{tl|Infobox church}}. It changes the font colour in the headings in that template to white for certain [[基督教派系|denominations]] of the church specified in the template, according to the following scheme:

<center>
{| class=wikitable
|-
! Religious Affiliation
! Colour
|-
| style="font-size:90%;" | <nowiki>[[聖公宗]], [[英格蘭教會]], [[威爾斯教會]], [[美國聖公會]], [[蘇格蘭聖公會]]</nowiki>
| style="background:#BC50A5; color:white" | #BC50A5
|-
| style="font-size:90%;" | <nowiki>[[靈恩運動]]</nowiki>
| style="background:#FF0000; color:white" | #FF0000
|-
| style="font-size:90%;" | <nowiki>[[信義宗]]</nowiki>
| style="background:#228B22; color:white" | #228B22
|-
| style="font-size:90%;" | <nowiki>[[循道宗]], [[英國循道會]], [[Primitive Methodism|Primitive Methodist]], [[Wesleyan Church|Wesleyan Methodist]]</nowiki>
| style="background:#CC6666; color:white;" | #CC6666
|-
| style="font-size:90%;" | ''Everything else defaults to''
| style="background:#CCCC99;" | #CCCC99
|}
</center>

For the full list of heading background colours, see {{tl|Infobox church/denomination}}.

Before changing the font colour in this template, please discuss the matter with other editors at "[[Template talk:Infobox church]]". Thanks.

